# Cursor Rules for Bug Bounty Swarm

always_read: ["CLAUDE.md", "skills/recon/SKILL.md"]
rate_limit: 10  # requests per second max
scope_check: required
destructive_actions: forbidden
auto_submit: false

coding_standards:
  - Use async Python (asyncio + aiohttp)
  - Type hints on all functions
  - Docstrings on all classes and methods
  - Error handling: never let one agent crash the swarm
  - All HTTP via aiohttp.ClientSession with timeout=30
